    LdeLauncher, Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig

    public class DynamicLauncher
extends SeleniumLauncher
    This class extends SeleniumLauncher to allow the launched UI to be determined (and reconfigured) at runtime via the setComponentToLaunch method.
    Since:
    1.2.0
    Author:
    Joshua Barclay
